</td>
<td>There are two versions or recensions by different <a href="/wiki/Shakha" title="Shakha">Shakhas</a>: <a href="/wiki/Madhyandina_Shakha" title="Madhyandina Shakha">Madhyandina</a> and <a href="/wiki/Kanva_Shakha" title="Kanva Shakha">Kanva</a>.
