<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Yajurveda_3">Yajurveda</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Brahmana&amp;action=edit&amp;section=43" title="Edit section: Yajurveda"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
